    (1699, 186, 83, 'I deserve this scholarship because I am a student mother who is determined to pursue education despite the many challenges I face. Balancing my responsibilities as a parent and as a student requires discipline, sacrifice, and strong time management skills. Even with limited resources, I continue to strive for academic excellence because I believe education is the key to building a better future for my child and myself.
This scholarship would greatly help ease my financial burden and allow me to focus more on my studies while providing for my family. More than financial support, it would serve as motivation for me to continue working hard and to become a role model for my child—showing that perseverance, education, and determination can overcome any obstacle. With this opportunity, I am committed to finishing my education and giving back to my community in the future.'),
