    (4751, 372, 147, '1st Year'),
    (4752, 372, 148, 'Why I Deserve to Be a Scholar

My name is Jea Princess M. Picon, and I am applying for a scholarship at Davao Vision Colleges, Inc. I am applying because my family is facing financial difficulties, and I want to continue my studies.

At present, all members of my family are unemployed, which makes it hard for us to support my education. Our home is located in Barangay Lamanan, Calinan District, which is far from the school and adds to our daily expenses. Because of this, it is not easy for my family to afford my tuition and transportation.

Even with these challenges, I am doing my best to study hard because I believe education will help me build a better future and support my family someday. A scholarship would be a big help for me to continue my studies without being a heavy burden to my family.

I hope to be given this opportunity, and I promise to use it wisely and do my best as a student.'),
